<br>
I do not think that people in the United States are there yet, so to speak. <br>
<br>
However in terms of &quot;relative&quot; opportunity, the US really does stand out. <br>
<br>
I think you need the higher, absolute standard, before you really attain the best possible status for the social contract between society and gov't. <br>
<br>
Finally, this &quot;absolute&quot; standard is going to be something that changes. It used to be that speaking from a general perspective, just a high school diploma was adequate if you were speaking of attaining the highest echelons of success. Now that simply is not the case. For every high school dropout come millionaire, there are 999 who float between min wage jobs or languish on welfare rolls. It's about the averages, not the exceptions.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raolfcq>RaolfCQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 1063<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/03 5:54:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=9>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for the Libertarians</span><hr size=1> I don't think we really disagree then.  Gogo Social Democracy! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=truthreason>TruthReason</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I'm actually Goanad.</span><br>  Posts: 1054<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/03 6:22:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for the Libertarians</span><hr size=1> It's just that the extremes for social democracy are staggering. <br>
